Language : c++

Main files : server.cpp, client.cpp, Makefile, sha256.h, Readme and the files generated
by thrift.


How to run and some sample output:

1. start the server first using : ./server port_number
2. based on the server machine, remote08 for example, start the client
with required parameter (see the following example)

Sample running and output:
1.commands:
run the command on remote08 : 1) ./server 3030 2) ./server 3031
run the following commands in order:

2: client
./client_request 3030 write <filename>
./client_request 3030 delete <filename>
./client_request 3030 read <filename>
